                                            </li>
                                            <li className="mb-2">
                                                â€¢ Write detailed description to set clear
                                                expectations
                                            </li>
                                            <li className="mb-0">
                                                â€¢ Choose relevant tags to improve discoverability
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
